These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, thriller
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, mexican
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | fanta    |
| Movie-Genre           | thriller | western |
| Nationality   | italian       | mexican  |
| Pet     | hedgehog      | dog     |

