.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, r&b
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, tiparillo
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, baseball
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | watermelon | cauliflower |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | r&b         |
| Cigar           | tiparillo     | bongani         |
| Sport     | baseball    | volleyball    |

