.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, sailing
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, project-manager
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Sport         | sailing          | climbing |
| Job           | project-manager | analyst     |
| Flower   | bellflower            | marigold         |
| Transport     | scooter         | quad-bike   |

