2. the person traveling to hamburg is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| City      | hamburg     | prague   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | action |
| Flower   | orchid   | dahlia |
| Pet           | hamster | rat    |

