.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, turkish
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, papaya
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, drama
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, taxi
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the british##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Nationality      | turkish     | british |
| Food          | papaya   | eggplant |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | documentary     |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi     |

 